text: Aída Nabila Román Arroyo (born May 21, 1988) is a Mexican archer. Román competed at the 2008, 2012, 2016, and the 2020 Summer Olympics.Aída Román == References == Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican archers Category:Olympic medalists for Mexico Category:Olympic silver medalists Category:Sportspeople from Mexico City
